                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lp-security-item">
                        <div class="lp-security-item-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 2a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a3 3 0 106 0V4a2 2 0 00-2-2H4zm1 14a1 1 0 100-2 1 1 0 000 2zm5-1.757l4.9-4.9a2 2 0 000-2.828L13.485 5.1a2 2 0 00-2.828 0L10 5.757v8.486zM16 18H9.071l6-6H16a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Complete audit trail</strong>
